12enum {
13 HOSTAPD_ACL_REJECT = 0,
14 HOSTAPD_ACL_ACCEPT = 1,
15 HOSTAPD_ACL_PENDING = 2,
16 HOSTAPD_ACL_ACCEPT_TIMEOUT = 3
17};
18
19int hostapd_check_acl(struct hostapd_data *hapd, const u8 *addr,
20 struct vlan_description *vlan_id);

22 const u8 *msg, size_t len, u32 *session_timeout,
23 u32 *acct_interim_interval,

26 char **identity, char **radius_cui,
27 int is_probe_req);
28int hostapd_acl_init(struct hostapd_data *hapd);
29void hostapd_acl_deinit(struct hostapd_data *hapd);
30void hostapd_free_psk_list(struct hostapd_sta_wpa_psk_short *psk);
31void hostapd_acl_expire(struct hostapd_data *hapd);

33#endif /* IEEE802_11_AUTH_H */
